></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>多个的点击与匿名回调</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C#\" data-language=\"C#\"><code class=\"language-C#\">Button[] btns &#x3D; GetComponentsInChildren&lt;Button&gt;();\nforeach (Button btn in btns)\n&#123;\n  switch (btn.name)\n  &#123;\n    case &quot;GotoAnotherPanelBtn&quot;:\n      btn.onClick.AddListener(delegate ()\n      &#123;\n        Debug.Log(&quot;切换控制面板&quot;);\n      &#125;);\n      break;\n    case &quot;ExitBtn&quot;:\n      btn.onClick.AddListener(delegate ()\n      &#123;\n        Debug.Log(&quot;退出该面板&quot;);\n      &#125;);\n      break;\n  &#125;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>UI的隐藏</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C#\" data-language=\"C#\"><code class=\"language-C#\">&#x2F;&#x2F;将它Destroy\nDestroy(this.gameObject);\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","text":"根据类型获取某个对象 &#x2F;&#x2F;这里我们找的是Canvas这个对象，该函数只找到一个 Canvas canvas &#x3D; FindObjectOfType&lt;Canvas&gt;(); 获取预制体 &#x2F;&#x2F;获取预制体 &#x2F;&#x2F...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Unity3d","slug":"Unity3d","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Unity3d.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Unity3d","slug":"Unity3d","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Unity3d.json"},{"name":"学习","slug":"学习","count":3,"path":"api/tags/学习.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"懒懒瑭岚","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/post/java期末复习/1761bac35e69253aa2999ff26b7ed6bbf63c8a8a.jpg@100Q.webp","link":"/","description":"平平无奇的博客","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stac